<br>
Now playing my 28 necro last night for hours my darkness never droped from me casting lifetap.  I don't think there is a sudden bug making dd break darkness, maybe just that proc?  <br>
<br>
I don't have a SBD but I am casting the spell engulfing darkness and using both siphon life and shock of poison.<br>
<br>
